msgid ""
"Content is stored as JSON. Examples:<br><strong>Heading:</strong> {\"text\":"
" \"My Title\", \"tag\": \"h2\", \"size\": \"xl\"}<br><strong>Text:</strong> "
"{\"text\": \"Your content here\", \"size\": "
"\"base\"}<br><strong>Button:</strong> {\"text\": \"Click Me\", \"url\": "
"\"/link/\", \"style\": \"primary\"}<br><strong>Image:</strong> {\"src\": "
"\"/path/to/image.jpg\", \"alt\": \"Description\"}"
msgstr ""
"เนื้อหาถูกจัดเก็บเป็น JSON ตัวอย่าง:<br><strong>หัวข้อ:</strong> {\"text\": "
"\"My Title\", \"tag\": \"h2\", \"size\": "
"\"xl\"}<br><strong>ข้อความ:</strong> {\"text\": \"Your content here\", "
"\"size\": \"base\"}<br><strong>ปุ่ม:</strong> {\"text\": \"Click Me\", "
"\"url\": \"/link/\", \"style\": \"primary\"}<br><strong>รูปภาพ:</strong> "
"{\"src\": \"/path/to/image.jpg\", \"alt\": \"Description\"}"

